      "**Wednesday – 13:33**",
      "Last year, in these very moments and days, I could not form any clear image in my mind of where I would be at this exact time the following year.\nI had stepped onto a path filled with excitement, motivation, hope, fear, ambiguity, and an uneven mixture of many other emotions.",
