      "I am constantly fleeing from routine, stability, and a defined course.\nAs soon as a pattern becomes fixed and repetitive, I do everything in my power to change it and disrupt it.",
      "It is as if, unconsciously, despite all my fears and anxieties, I am always trying to push myself outside my safe zone in any possible way.",
      "Apparently this is an important, valuable, even beneficial trait.\nAnd in truth, it has been.",
