      "Perhaps sometimes a safe zone is necessary.\nPerhaps stability also has its value.\nPerhaps it is good for a person to pause for a moment and rest within a healthy and secure framework, and enjoy it-rather than destroying it in hope of discovering greater joy and excitement in the next stage.",
